Currently working on a family video for this trip. I&amp;rsquo;ll post it here, once it&amp;rsquo;s finished. I make family memory videos of every trip we go on. You can find them all here.</description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Just got back home after a long trip to Glacier and Canada.
Had lots of fun, went to the Sun Road, Banff, Lake Louise, and saw quite a few bears in Canada.</p>
<p>Currently working on a family video for this trip.
I&rsquo;ll post it here, once it&rsquo;s finished.
I make family memory videos of every trip we go on.
